    "body": "Fix build errors, enhance site navigation (header, footer, sidebar), and resolve broken links to improve site functionality and user experience.\n\nThe project initially failed to build due to several TypeScript errors, including duplicate tags and prop type mismatches. These were resolved, and type safety was improved in service components. Additionally, the header, footer, and sidebar were significantly restructured to provide more comprehensive and organized navigation, addressing numerous broken links and adding missing routes for better site discoverability and user flow.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-715661ec-4513-4bd9-afc6-000b095af31a\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-715661ec-4513-4bd9-afc6-000b095af31a\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
