    "body": "Resolve critical build errors, refactor application routing, and clean up the sitemap structure.\n\nThe application was encountering numerous build failures due to JSX syntax errors, incorrect component usage (e.g., `PerformanceOptimizer` as a wrapper), merge conflicts in `Sitemap.tsx`, and widespread TypeScript errors stemming from duplicate imports, non-existent page references, and prop mismatches. This PR systematically addresses these issues to restore a functional build and improve code maintainability.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-f3ba2a85-1e9f-438d-9f07-3a3f50cbbcfb\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-f3ba2a85-1e9f-438d-9f07-3a3f50cbbcfb\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
