    "body": "Add new advanced and emerging micro SAAS, IT, and AI services with dedicated showcase pages to diversify product offerings and improve discoverability.\n\nThe existing service portfolio was expanded with 10 new cutting-edge services focusing on AI, Quantum Computing, Autonomous Systems, Blockchain, Legal Tech, Sustainability, Cybersecurity, Smart Cities, and Healthcare. Additionally, the existing emerging tech services were updated to a standardized data structure, and two new pages (`AdvancedInnovativeServices` and `ComprehensiveServicesShowcase`) were created to provide a detailed and searchable overview of all innovative offerings, complete with features, benefits, pricing, and contact information.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-aeb1356d-a451-4a9d-a80f-cc40a187c1b6\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-aeb1356d-a451-4a9d-a80f-cc40a187c1b6\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
