    "body": "Fix broken links and improve site navigation by adding new AI service pages and updating routing.\n\nThe previous website analysis identified 278 broken links, primarily due to missing content and incorrect hash-based navigation for service pages. This PR addresses these issues by creating 6 critical AI service pages, establishing dedicated routes for them, and updating the Header, Footer, and Sidebar components to use direct, functional links, thereby resolving the identified navigation issues and improving overall site discoverability.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-22c8bd15-8cd7-417c-8fdc-0088a8fd997c\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-22c8bd15-8cd7-417c-8fdc-0088a8fd997c\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
