    "body": "Add new AI, Quantum, Blockchain, and Edge Computing services with futuristic design enhancements to expand the service portfolio and improve user experience.\n\nThe changes implement the core task requirements by introducing several new cutting-edge service pages, integrating them into the navigation and home page, and applying advanced CSS for a modern, responsive, and visually appealing interface. This significantly diversifies the app's offerings and enhances its overall presentation.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-3a1bcad8-6395-4cbf-8e93-efd242766219\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-3a1bcad8-6395-4cbf-8e93-efd242766219\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
