    "body": "Add 15+ new diversified micro SAAS, IT, and AI services with dedicated showcase pages to expand the product portfolio and improve service discoverability.\n\nThis PR introduces a significant expansion of Zion Tech Group's service offerings, including:\n- 5 Advanced AI Services (e.g., Edge AI, Federated Learning, Quantum ML)\n- 5 Innovative IT Infrastructure Services (e.g., Green Computing, Quantum-Ready Infra, Zero-Trust Security)\n- 5 Innovative Micro SAAS Solutions (e.g., Web3 Business Platform, Metaverse Solutions, AI Content Creation)\n\nNew pages (`/innovative-services-showcase` and `/comprehensive-overview`) have been added to effectively present these services, including features, benefits, market prices, ROI, and contact information, as requested by the task. The changes also include the necessary data structures and routing to support these new additions.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-cd16f75d-18cd-4920-bb67-ef61b066ede1\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-cd16f75d-18cd-4920-bb67-ef61b066ede1\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
