    "body": "Fix broken links and improve site navigation by adding new pages and updating header, footer, and sidebar components.\n\nThe initial analysis revealed 278 broken links and missing content. This PR addresses these issues by creating key missing pages (e.g., AI Research Assistant, SOC2 Compliance, Quantum Neural Network Platform, AI Business Solutions, Sitemap) and integrating them into the site's navigation across the header, footer, and sidebar for a more robust and user-friendly experience.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-854127e1-6c76-4850-b43c-e31d15b3bacf\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-854127e1-6c76-4850-b43c-e31d15b3bacf\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
