    "body": "Fixes and hardens GitHub Actions workflows by resolving YAML syntax errors, improving security, and standardizing configurations.\n\nThis PR addresses various issues across GitHub Actions workflows, including:\n- **Security:** Switched `pull_request_target` to `pull_request` and added explicit `contents: read` permissions where appropriate.\n- **YAML Syntax:** Corrected numerous parsing errors such as stray characters, incorrect indentation, duplicate blocks, and improper quoting.\n- **Standardization:** Updated `actions/checkout` and `actions/setup-node` to `v4`, standardized Node.js versions, and improved script robustness (e.g., replacing heredocs).\nAll workflows now pass YAML validation.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-4573d548-3db6-4286-81a2-b9c02d5083fe\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-4573d548-3db6-4286-81a2-b9c02d5083fe\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
