    "body": "Created key missing pages and updated navigation components to fix broken links and improve site structure.\n\nThis PR addresses a significant portion of the identified broken links and missing content by implementing four critical new pages: `5G Enterprise Solutions`, `AI Autonomous Business Manager`, `AI Autonomous Business Platform`, and `AI Autonomous Research Assistant`. Corresponding navigation links have been added and corrected in the Header, Footer, and Sidebar components to ensure these new pages are accessible and the overall site navigation is improved. Build issues encountered during development were also resolved.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-32b4d22d-50b4-455b-ab6e-7aa91c41cda7\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-32b4d22d-50b4-455b-ab6e-7aa91c41cda7\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
