    "body": "Add missing AI service pages and update global navigation (header, footer, sidebar) and routing.\n\nThe website analysis revealed several missing pages and inconsistent routing. This PR addresses these by creating dedicated pages for AI Business Intelligence, AI HR & Recruitment, AI Healthcare Analytics, AI Legal Tech, AI Machine Learning, and AI Marketing Automation. The `App.tsx` routing has been updated to include these new pages, and the `Header.tsx`, `Footer.tsx`, and `Sidebar.tsx` components have been refactored to provide organized and correct links, enhancing overall site navigation and user experience.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-942bb8ce-a508-4cb5-ba4f-302d69d7f07f\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-942bb8ce-a508-4cb5-ba4f-302d69d7f07f\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
