    "body": "feat: Add new service pages and fix Home.tsx export\n\nAdds new pages for 5G Enterprise Solutions, AI Autonomous Research Assistant, AI-Powered IT Asset Management, Autonomous Business Operations Platform, Quantum Neural Network Platform, SOC2 Compliance Automation, and an About page. Also fixes a missing default export in `Home.tsx`.\n\nThese additions resolve broken links (404 errors), enhance content quality, and improve the website's professional appearance and SEO by providing dedicated, comprehensive pages for previously referenced but non-existent services. The `Home.tsx` fix ensures the project builds successfully.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-9f3e96b2-249a-48f6-ba40-7cabf4391ad6\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-9f3e96b2-249a-48f6-ba40-7cabf4391ad6\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
