    "body": "Add a comprehensive suite of new micro SAAS, IT, and AI services to expand the Zion Tech Group's portfolio and enhance service advertising.\n\nThe task requested a significant expansion of service offerings, including detailed features, benefits, pricing, and contact information, without altering existing services. This PR introduces over 30 new cutting-edge services across various categories (Quantum AI, Neurotechnology, Climate AI, Space Tech, Digital Twin, Metaverse, Edge AI, Synthetic Biology, Quantum Internet, Advanced IT Infrastructure, Specialized AI) and integrates them into the application's overview and a new showcase page.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-01b8a183-8570-46bf-a9f5-b6cdee8983ce\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-01b8a183-8570-46bf-a9f5-b6cdee8983ce\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
