    "body": "Implement comprehensive website enhancements including updated sitemap, improved SEO, advanced accessibility features, and performance monitoring to boost discoverability, user experience, and efficiency.\n\nThis PR addresses a multi-faceted analysis report that highlighted critical areas for improvement:\n*   **Broken Links**: The sitemap generation script was overhauled to accurately reflect current routes and remove outdated entries, resolving numerous broken links.\n*   **SEO Optimization**: The `EnhancedSEO` component now provides more granular control over meta tags and structured data, directly improving search engine visibility.\n*   **Performance**: The `PerformanceOptimizer` focuses on real-time Core Web Vitals monitoring and basic image optimization, providing insights and foundational improvements for site speed.\n*   **User Experience**: The `EnhancedAccessibility` component introduces a robust set of tools for high contrast, large text, reduced motion, screen reader support, keyboard navigation, and color blind modes, significantly improving the site's inclusivity.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-3b760019-0249-40f9-b20c-dd482504643d\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-3b760019-0249-40f9-b20c-dd482504643d\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
