    "body": "Enhance website components (Header, Hero, Home, Footer) to improve user experience, SEO, performance, and accessibility.\n\nThis PR implements comprehensive improvements based on a deep analysis of the website. Key changes include:\n*   **Header**: Added search functionality, enhanced services dropdown with feature tags, and improved accessibility.\n*   **Hero Section**: Integrated social proof elements, refined feature pills, and updated CTA for better engagement.\n*   **Home Page**: Introduced a \"Quick Actions\" section, detailed service cards with feature lists, enriched testimonials with company info, and updated SEO keywords.\n*   **Footer**: Reorganized sections, added company statistics, quick action links, enhanced social media links, and included security certifications for better trust and information architecture.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-ab8c529f-90da-4551-9eb3-d986546dee29\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-ab8c529f-90da-4551-9eb3-d986546dee29\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
