    "body": "Expand Zion Tech Group's service portfolio by adding 36+ new innovative micro SAAS, IT, and AI solutions with dedicated showcase pages.\n\nThis PR introduces new service data files across six categories (AI & Business Automation, Blockchain & Web3, Healthcare & Biotech, IoT & Smart City, Robotics & Automation, Quantum Computing), each with detailed features, market prices, ROI, and contact information. Two new pages (`/innovative-services-showcase` and `/comprehensive-services-overview`) were created and integrated into the routing to display these services. The PR also includes various dependency updates and code fixes (e.g., icon references, interface compatibility) to ensure the project builds successfully.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-1b2c52cc-03dd-4ea8-8b99-985231ac1855\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-1b2c52cc-03dd-4ea8-8b99-985231ac1855\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
