    "body": "Add diversified micro SAAS, IT, and AI services, and enhance the app with a futuristic design and improved navigation to expand offerings and user experience.\n\nThis PR implements a comprehensive update, fulfilling the user's request to significantly expand service offerings, introduce a futuristic aesthetic, and improve site usability, responsiveness, and content visibility across all pages. This includes creating a dedicated IT Services page, enriching existing Micro SAAS and AI service pages with more detailed and real solutions, and overhauling the header and footer for better navigation and a modern look.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-07d0dea6-2344-47c8-b6ed-5ac64238b0cf\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-07d0dea6-2344-47c8-b6ed-5ac64238b0cf\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
