    "body": "Expand service offerings with new Micro SAAS and IT Services, and implement a futuristic design overhaul to enhance user experience and site appeal.\n\nThis PR significantly diversifies the service catalog by adding 15+ new Micro SAAS solutions and a dedicated IT Services page with 12 comprehensive offerings, complete with detailed features, benefits, and pricing. Concurrently, it modernizes the entire application with a futuristic design, animated backgrounds, neon effects, and improved navigation, header, footer, and responsiveness, directly addressing the user's request for an innovative and visually appealing platform.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-33ef6559-49fb-4733-912f-6420457e417e\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-33ef6559-49fb-4733-912f-6420457e417e\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
