    "body": "Fix dependency issues and resolve merge conflicts to enable successful project builds and GitHub Actions.\n\nThe project was failing to build due to a `tailwind-merge` version mismatch, an unnecessary `husky` prepare script, and numerous merge conflicts across several UI components and the `Services.tsx` page. These issues were preventing GitHub Actions from running correctly. This PR addresses these critical build blockers.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-ed78fb8e-8575-4c97-a38a-62b8722af3e6\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-ed78fb8e-8575-4c97-a38a-62b8722af3e6\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
