    "body": "Introduce new AI, Micro SAAS, and IT services with a futuristic design system and refactored service presentation.\n\nThis PR significantly expands the service offerings with detailed, real-world solutions across AI, Micro SAAS, and IT categories. It also overhauls the site's aesthetic to a futuristic design, incorporating animated backgrounds, neon effects, and glassmorphism. The service display and navigation have been refactored to accommodate these new offerings and design principles, leading to the removal of several older, less integrated components to streamline the codebase and improve overall user experience and responsiveness.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-8c9b158a-6d26-44c9-ab30-08231bf8e081\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-8c9b158a-6d26-44c9-ab30-08231bf8e081\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
