    "body": "Implement comprehensive UI/UX and performance enhancements across the Zion Tech Group website.\n\nTo significantly improve user experience, site performance, and maintainability based on a deep analysis of the existing application and repository. This includes an enhanced Header with advanced navigation and search, a redesigned Footer with better social media integration, an optimized Home Page featuring an interactive hero section and performance improvements (lazy loading, memoization), and the introduction of a new `PerformanceOptimizer` component for real-time monitoring and suggestions.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-9ae2ede7-f960-4dcb-b512-e7cb6f69fb89\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-9ae2ede7-f960-4dcb-b512-e7cb6f69fb89\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\">\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\">\n    <img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n\n",
